OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSchools to cut staff in    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbudget squeeze, union says 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Many schools in England are considering
OL,6, cutting teachers or teaching hours to  
OL,7, save money, says the head teachers'    
OL,8, union, NAHT.                           
OL,10,FOf the 11,000 respondents to NAHT's    
OL,11,Fsnapshot survey, 66% said they will    
OL,12,Fhave to make teaching assistants       
OL,13,Fredundant or cut their hours. Half say 
OL,14,Fthey could do the same for teachers.   
OL,16,FSchool funding is increasing, but costs
OL,17,Fsuch as pay and energy are rising fast.
OL,19,FThe Department for Education has not   
OL,20,Fyet commented.                         
